{"type":null,"faqId":11976,"title":"G620-L72  屏幕自动黑屏，如何解决？","answer":"<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">通话过程中屏幕自动黑屏。</span> \n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">这是正常现象。手机听筒靠近头部时，听筒附近的接近光传感器被遮挡，屏幕自动关闭。当手机离开头部，屏幕自动点亮。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">为了保证手机的正常使用，请注意不要用手机套或其他物体遮挡听筒附近的屏幕。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">运行某些不兼容的第三方应用程序时屏幕黑屏。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">请卸载该应用程序或备份重要数据后将手机恢复出厂设置。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">同时运行过多应用程序可能会导致屏幕黑屏。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">关闭后台暂时不需要的应用程序：在主屏幕，点击“手机管理</span> <span>&gt; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机管家”，点击“手机加速”，一键结束后台运行的应用。</span> \n</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33372\" /> \n<p>\n\t&nbsp;<span>* </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":1,"unUseful":9,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2758","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398822209000,"seriesProductName":"G620-L72","visitedTimes":447,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"黑屏","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}